{"url": "https://www.ahlanlive.com/world-exclusive-william-reveals-why-fergie-left-the-black-eyed-peas-and-the-truth-about-nicole-scherzinger-619651.html", "text": "Ready for the return of The Black Eyed Peas? So are we! However, you may notice the line-up has changed a bit since we last saw them. Just a few days ago rumours started circulating that Fergie was possibly leaving the band, and that Nicole Scherzinger was replacing her. And now Ahlan! can reveal what\u2019s REALLY going\u2026\n\nWe spoke to The Black Eyed Peas (will.i.am, Taboo and apl.de.ap) ahead of their concert at the opening ceremony of the 2017 UEFA Champions League sponsored by Pepsi. Sadly, yes, Fergie has left the band. will.i.am explained the situation to us: \u201cSince the beginning of Black Eyed Peas, we\u2019ve always had amazing vocalists that appeared on the mic with us. People like Macy Gray, Esthero, Debi Nova, Fergie. On Elephunk, there were several females that appeared on that album. Obviously Fergie was the featured female, but on songs like Lets Get it Started, it\u2019s Noelle (Scaggs), and then Fergie, songs like Latin Girls, it\u2019s Debi Nova, and Request Line, it\u2019s Macy Gray. We\u2019ll always work with good females.\u201d\n\nThat\u2019s true, yes, but we can\u2019t help but feel that will.i.am is just dumping Fergie Ferg into a group of female artists the band has worked with in the past. For 15 years Fergie has played an enormous role as frontwoman, and her vocals are strongly featured on the majority of the band\u2019s biggest hits.\n\napl\n\nSo is Fergie being replaced? No, according to will.i.am. \u201cAs for replacing, what people know The Black Eyed Peas to be, nobody is replacing Fergie,\u201d he told us. \u201cShe\u2019s working on her solo project at the moment, we\u2019re on this brand-new experience, celebrating 20 years of Black Eyed Peas putting out music. We worked on a bunch of songs on her solo record, we\u2019re proud that she has her label, but Black Eyed Peas are pushing it forward in terms of content, technology and experiences on our new project, Masters of the Sun.\u201d\n\nIt was reported that none other than Nicole Scherzinger would be replacing Fergie, which quite honestly, we wouldn\u2019t mind at all. Although that\u2019s not on the cards, she is somehow involved. \u201cNicole is on the new BEP project as well,\u201d said will.i.am. \u201cI don\u2019t want to go into details how she\u2019s involved yet,\u201d he added.\n\nWe\u2019re sad Fergie won\u2019t be belting out hits like Where is the Love, Boom Boom Pow and I Gotta Feeling, but we look forward to seeing what the boys (AND Nicole Scherzinger) have up their sleeves.\n\nFor the full interview, don\u2019t miss next week\u2019s issue of Ahlan!", "images": ["https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/280px_250px_wide_landscape/public/images/2017/05/31/MINA-SEYAHI-IMG_1830.JPG?itok=WifXrYr1", "https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/280px_250px_wide_landscape/public/images/2014/11/27/459405060-%281%29.jpg?itok=t0dLBhE9", "https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/square_70/public/images/2019/11/11/Awards-_-ABE_-0370.jpeg?itok=eYw45ypZ", "https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/square_70/public/images/2019/10/10/paint-brush.jpg?itok=JhXlmNsZ&c=bf54ed928b1303832336d672ce111b56", "https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/280px_250px_wide_landscape/public/images/2014/10/13/wenn21822533.jpg?itok=kW3A4xkV", "https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/130px_95px_wide_landscape/public/images/2019/11/27/HOT100-2019_00_Cover.jpg?itok=bNZ3e8iy&c=f1b8c5b19d6cf1908989294ece7918fd", "https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/square_70/public/images/2019/10/28/13150995_1176218959109640_814085359_n.jpg?itok=F0PqTWp_", "https://www.ahlanlive.com/sites/default/files/styles/square_70/public/images/2019/10/13/shutterstock_587371247.jpg?itok=ouv_Xgw8&c=061af136aea958187e6bf860a9278188", "https: